<article id="article" class="article "><header><h1 class="title" itemprop="headline">Death by Text: The case against Michelle Carter</h1>

					<p class="dek">"48 Hours" had the groundbreaking trial of a crime of the digital age, and now the conclusion -- should a 20-year-old woman go to jail for sending texts?</p>
		
    </header><div class="social sharebar_expanded inline-sharebar theme-light  location-top" data-component="sharebar">

